WEBVTT

00:03:28.213 --> 00:03:31.475
But the other 2,000
better learn how to weld.

00:03:31.499 --> 00:03:33.951
(Laughter)

00:03:33.975 --> 00:03:35.998
Tell the kids the truth.

00:03:36.474 --> 00:03:39.268
You could be anything you're good at,

00:03:39.292 --> 00:03:40.609
(Laughter)

00:03:40.633 --> 00:03:42.387
as long as they're hiring.

00:03:42.411 --> 00:03:44.593
(Laughter)

00:03:44.617 --> 00:03:45.967
AG: The thing about passions

00:03:45.991 --> 00:03:48.410
is that we often settle on them
when we're young.

00:03:48.434 --> 00:03:50.522
The danger is getting locked in.

00:03:50.546 --> 00:03:52.371
Most of the time, our early passions

00:03:52.395 --> 00:03:54.895
are not the best guide
to our later careers.

00:03:54.919 --> 00:03:58.553
Maria Konnikova: There are so many things
about the future and about yourself

00:03:58.577 --> 00:03:59.831
that you don't understand.

00:03:59.855 --> 00:04:02.355
You don't know what future you
is going to be like.